'From Squeak 2.0 of May 22, 1998 on 15 June 1998 at 3:49:28 pm'!"Change Set:		possessiveTileDate:			15 June 1998Author:			Scott WallaceMakes the wording of any object-ref tile show the possessive ending if and only if it is a slot-reference on the object.  Caution:  will not fix up old tiles that predate this fix, only applies to scripts created after this fix is present"!!TileMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 6/11/1998 17:58'!bePossessive	self setProperty: #possessive toValue: true.	self line1: actualObject externalName, '''s'! !!TileMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 6/11/1998 18:00'!bringUpToDate	| newLabel |	type == #objRef ifTrue:		[newLabel _ actualObject externalName.		self isPossessive ifTrue:			[newLabel _ newLabel, '''s'].		self line1: newLabel]	! !!TileMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 6/11/1998 17:58'!isPossessive	^ self hasProperty: #possessive! !!TilePadMorph methodsFor: 'all' stamp: 'sw 6/15/1998 09:21'!acceptDroppingMorph: aMorph event: evt	| editor wasPossessive |	wasPossessive _ submorphs size > 0 and: [submorphs first isPossessive].	self prepareToUndoDropOf: aMorph.	self removeAllMorphs.	aMorph position: self position.	self addMorph: aMorph.	wasPossessive ifTrue: [aMorph bePossessive].	(editor _ self topEditor) ifNotNil: [editor install]! !